# All of Your Questions About ITIN Mortgages Answered

**Author:** First Pryority Bank  
**Original Link:** [Read the full post here](https://firstpryoritybank.com/all-of-your-questions-about-itin-mortgages-answered/)

## Summary

This blog post from First Pryority Bank answers common questions about ITIN (Individual Taxpayer Identification Number) mortgages. It explains what an ITIN mortgage is, who may qualify, and how it can help non-citizen residents or individuals without a Social Security Number buy a home.

The article covers eligibility requirements, documentation, and the benefits and considerations of using an ITIN mortgage.

## Highlights

- What an ITIN mortgage is and who it serves.
- Key steps and documentation needed to apply.
- Tips for working with lenders familiar with ITIN loans.

For more information, visit the [original article](https://firstpryoritybank.com/all-of-your-questions-about-itin-mortgages-answered/).

